{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.760", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.640", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.320", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Immer deutlicher zeigte sich im Verlauf dieses Jahres, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.960", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die AfD in den Bundestag einziehen w\u00fcrde und dass sie auch den Alterspr\u00e4sidenten stellen w\u00fcrde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.640", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil sie neben vielen jungen Abgeordneten eben auch den \u00e4ltesten Abgeordneten mit an Bord hatte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.240", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als dies deutlich wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00e4nderten Sie hier im alten Bundestag ganz schnell die Gesch\u00e4ftsordnung\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.720", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "knapp vor der Wahl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zwei Wochen vor Ende Sitzungsperiode. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.720", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das war ein so durchsichtiges Man\u00f6ver; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das lassen wir Ihnen hier nicht durchgehen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.960", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine List, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.720", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit der Sie die AfD ausgrenzen wollten! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.760", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das kann so nicht weitergehen!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.840", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die AfD hatte gerade den 13.\u00a0Wahlsieg in Folge erzielt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.600", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine Triumphserie bei Landtagswahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.600", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die so zuvor keine Partei nach ihrer Gr\u00fcndung erzielt hatte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.200", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der alte Bundestag aber \u00e4nderte die Gesch\u00e4ftsordnung pl\u00f6tzlich so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.040", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nicht mehr der \u00e4lteste Abgeordnete, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern der mit der l\u00e4ngsten Dienstzeit die erste Sitzung als Alterspr\u00e4sident er\u00f6ffnen sollte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und das w\u00fcrde dann nicht mehr ein AfD-Abgeordneter sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.760", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie begr\u00fcndeten dies damit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass nur der dienst\u00e4lteste Abgeordnete eine korrekte Sitzungsleitung sicherstellen k\u00f6nne. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.880", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war das Argument. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.040", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.920", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.440", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "seit 1848 ist in Deutschland Tradition, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.160", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die konstituierende Sitzung nat\u00fcrlich vom \u00e4ltesten Mitglied der Versammlung er\u00f6ffnet wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.840", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das war eine Tradition von der Frankfurter Paulskirche bis Gustav Stresemann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.800", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Adenauer \u00fcber Brandt bis Kohl, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ja bis zu der ersten Regierung Merkel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alle Reichstage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.280", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "alle Bundestage konnten dem Argument \u201eDienstalter\u201c nichts abgewinnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ja auch klar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In 150\u00a0Jahren Parlamentsgeschichte blieb die Regel des Alterspr\u00e4sidenten unangetastet."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unangetastet? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.120", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gab eine Ausnahme: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.400", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "1933 hat Hermann G\u00f6ring die Regel gebrochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil er politische Gegner ausgrenzen wollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.880", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "damals Clara Zetkin."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.520", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie sich auf solch schiefe Bahn begeben? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.040", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommen Sie zur\u00fcck auf die Linie der gro\u00dfen deutschen Demokraten! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu fordere ich Sie hier auf."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.920", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn stets er\u00f6ffnete der Parlamentarier, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.200", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der aufgrund von Lebenserfahrung und Altersweisheit Versammlungen besonders umsichtig er\u00f6ffnen konnte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.480", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das waren die Idee und die Tradition \u00fcber 150\u00a0Jahre. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.720", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Denn zur blo\u00dfen Er\u00f6ffnung ist ja kein geballtes Gesch\u00e4ftsordnungswissen vonn\u00f6ten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.080", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird sofort ein Versammlungspr\u00e4sident gew\u00e4hlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.720", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der versiert in der Sache ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.600", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch deshalb ist Ihr Argument, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Dienst\u00e4lteste m\u00fcsse aus fachlichen Gr\u00fcnden er\u00f6ffnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schlichtweg unsinnig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.200", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Selbst die Presse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.280", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die uns ja nicht durchg\u00e4ngig gewogen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.160", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warnte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.720", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
